membershipSuspension.suspensionRuleNote1: Free arrangements can be made if a member applies for a suspension in the circumstances listed in Clause G1a and G1b below
membershipSuspension.suspensionRuleNote1a: if you are pregnant during your contract validity, your membership may be suspended for a maximum of twelve (12) months with a written certificate issued by a medical doctor; or
membershipSuspension.suspensionRuleNote1b: if you have other medical reasons with a written certificate issued by a medical doctor to prove you are not suitable for any physical activity; you may suspend your membership until the date indicated in your medical certificate.
membershipSuspension.suspensionRuleNote2: For any other reason for suspension, member will be charged HKD$200 per month (this fee may be adjusted at the discretion of Square Group). The suspension fee is non-refundable and non transferable. Square Group reserves every right to reject any suspension request at its discretion. Member can apply a maximum of three (3) months and a minimum of one (1) month for each suspension. You are allowed to suspend your Agreement twice within the Minimum Payment Term.
membershipSuspension.suspensionRuleNote3: If a member wishes to start the suspension period during the month where he / she has made a payment, please note suspension will not be activated until the next payment month and the member will still be entitled to the use of the Facilities during the month he / she has made payment.

exploreSquareFitness.title1: Fitness Programmes with All Day Access - Your Ultimate Workout Safe Space
exploreSquareFitness.title3: Diverse Programs - Be Versatile With Square
exploreSquareFitness.title5: Community Engagement - Be Fair; Be Square
exploreSquareFitness.title6: Free Trial Gym Experience - Enjoy Your One-Day Gym Pass
exploreSquareFitness.subTitle1: At Square Fitness, we understand that your schedule is unique, and so should your fitness routine. Our day-pass gym options and 24-hour locations are designed to accommodate the busiest of lifestyles in Hong Kong. Whether you prefer a refreshing morning workout or a late-night session, our gym rooms are always open and ready for you. With Square Fitness, you never have to compromise on your fitness goals; we strive to break through your physical limits. Our around-the-clock availability ensures that you can work out at your convenience, embracing a gym-fit lifestyle that suits you best.
exploreSquareFitness.subTitle2: We believe that high-quality fitness should be accessible to everyone with flexible membership terms and reasonable prices. Square Fitness offers an upscale environment complete with well-ventilated spaces to enhance the comfort of your workouts. We pride ourselves on our comprehensive, well-rounded fitness programs tailored to various fitness levels and interests. Moreover, we provide top-notch personal training with our highly skilled and knowledgeable teams to reach your fitness goals. Experience the perfect blend of quality and affordability at Square Fitness.
exploreSquareFitness.subTitle3: To achieve a unique and diverse fitness journey, Square Fitness offers a variety of gym fitness programs and services for our members. From the intensity of bodybuilding to the tranquility of yoga, our expert trainers craft personalized plans to cater to your fitness needs. Whether you are a gym beginner or an experienced athlete, our center provides the top fitness guidance and machines to fit your goals. Explore our diverse programs and find the one that resonates with you.
exploreSquareFitness.subTitle4: Is fitness merely effective in empowering your physical abilities? We believe fitness is a process of working yourself towards health and happiness. Square Fitness emphasizes a comprehensive approach that goes beyond the gym room. By offering interlocking services from massage therapy, stretching sessions, to nutrition guidance, we accompany you to the best self thoroughly. Get your feet wet with us and embrace an unprecedented fitness journey now!
exploreSquareFitness.subTitle5: Being part of Square Fitness means being part of a community that shares your passion for fitness. We foster a vibrant environment where members can connect, learn, and grow together. Our fitness studio hosts different yoga workshops and classes to encourage community engagement. Join us, participate in our challenges, and connect with like-minded individuals who are on the same journey as you. At Square Fitness, you're not just joining a gym; you're joining a family that supports and celebrates your success.
exploreSquareFitness.subTitle6: Choosing the right fitness studio is a crucial decision, and we want you to feel confident about joining the Square Fitness family. That's why we offer a free trial gym pass, allowing you to experience our world-class facilities, meet our trainers, and immerse yourself in our community. Our free trial gym is more than just a sneak peek; it's an invitation to discover a gym room experience that's tailored to you. Come and see for yourself what makes Square Fitness stand out. We're confident that once you try, you'll want to stay.
exploreSquareFitness.subTitle6a: For the latest offer please contact our sales.
